title: AWS ECS: Clusters Summary
agents: aws
catalog: cloud/aws
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors all AWS ECS clusters and reports
 a summary of their states.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related
 special agent {Amazon Web Services (AWS)}.

 The service goes {WARN} if at least one cluster is in state failed.

 Otherwise the service is {OK}.

discovery:
 One service is created.
